---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection

    title="Major Races"

    subtitle="The people who call Solmara home."

>

<div class="race-grid">

    <article class="race-card">

        <h3>Humans</h3>

        <p class="status">Majority</p>

        <p>

            The dominant people of Solmara, forming the backbone of its kingdoms,
            commerce, agriculture, and government.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="race-card">

        <h3>Beastkin</h3>

        <p class="status">Common</p>

        <p>

            Integrated throughout Solmara, Beastkin contribute to every aspect
            of society, from farming and craftsmanship to military service.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="race-card">

        <h3>Demi-Humans</h3>

        <p class="status">Common</p>

        <p>

            Found across towns and cities, Demi-Humans enrich Solmara's diverse
            communities through countless professions and traditions.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="race-card">

        <h3>Elves</h3>

        <p class="status">Rare</p>

        <p>

            Though welcomed, elves are uncommon in Solmara, with most tracing
            their origins to the Thorne Empire.

        </p>

    </article>

</div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.race-grid{

    display:grid;

    grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);

    gap:2rem;

}

.race-card{

    padding:2.5rem;

    border-radius:20px;

    border:1px solid rgba(198,166,107,.15);

    background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);

    transition:.35s;

}

.race-card:hover{

    transform:translateY(-8px);

    border-color:var(--primary);

}

.race-card h3{

    font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

    font-size:2rem;

    color:white;

    margin-bottom:.5rem;

}

.status{

    color:var(--primary);

    text-transform:uppercase;

    letter-spacing:.25em;

    font-size:.75rem;

    margin-bottom:1.5rem;

}

.race-card p{

    color:var(--muted);

    line-height:1.9;

}

@media(max-width:768px){

.race-grid{

    grid-template-columns:1fr;

}

}

</style>